iginal_language":"es"},{"id":462,"adult":false,"title":"Erin Brockovich","video":false,"overview":"A twice-divorced mother of three who sees an injustice, takes on the bad guy and wins -- with a little help from her push-up bra. Erin goes to work for an attorney and comes across medical records describing illnesses clustered in one nearby town. She starts investigating and soon exposes a monumental cover-up.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":4.8383,"vote_count":3561,"poster_path":"/jEMvWBWVjndZT0vJnLrRWi9ajea.jpg","release_date":"2000-03-17","vote_average":7.437,"backdrop_path":"/3HmLKhahTxX2ALTWlagr92pZrU7.jpg","original_title":"Erin Brockovich","original_language":"en"},{"id":46738,"adult":false,"title":"Incendies","video":false,"overview":"A mother's last wishes send twins Jeanne and Simon on a journey to Middle East in search of their tangled roots. Adapted from Wajdi Mouawad's acclaimed play, Incendies tells the powerful and moving tale of two young adults' voyage to the core of deep-rooted hatred, never-ending wars and enduring love.","genre_ids":[18,10752,9648],"media_type":"movie","popularity":11.5515,"vote_count":3160,"poster_path":"/yH6DAQVgbyj72S66gN4WWVoTjuf.jpg","release_date":"2010-09-17","vote_average":8.106,"backdrop_path":"/f3ATwil5vmUeTsogBaMEKbBYBth.jpg","original_title":"Incendies","original_language":"fr"},{"id":567748,"adult":false,"title":"The Guilty","video":false,"overview":"A demoted police officer assigned to a call dispatch desk is conflicted when he receives an emergency phone call from a kidnapped woman.","genre_ids":[18,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":4.3836,"vote_count":3017,"poster_path":"/m8aR1k35oZMOzZ1kYWUyt401mwq.jpg","release_date":"2021-09-24","vote_average":6.423,"backdrop_path":"/5wPWgTvdoVKW6ICeEAg86IBJOBW.jpg","original_title":"The Guilty","original_language":"en"},{"id":524047,"adult":false,"title":"Greenland","video":false,"overview":"John Garrity, his estranged wife and their young son embark on a perilous journey to find sanctuary as a planet-killing comet hurtles toward Earth. Amid terrifying accounts of cities getting levelled, the Garritys experience the best and worst in humanity. As the countdown to the global apocalypse approaches zero, their incredible trek culminates in a desperate and last-minute flight to a possible safe haven.","genre_ids":[28,12,53,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":20.1674,"vote_count":5096,"poster_path":"/bNo2mcvSwIvnx8K6y1euAc1TLVq.jpg","release_date":"2020-07-29","vote_average":7.128,"backdrop_path":"/uorMP2U1F0AfogYMz4lYu2EbgYo.jpg","original_title":"Greenland","original_language":"en"},{"id":575265,"adult":false,"title":"Mission: Impossible - The Final Reckoning","video":false,"overview":"Ethan Hunt and team continue their search for the terrifying AI known as the Entity — which has infiltrated intelligence networks all over the globe — with the world's governments and a mysterious ghost from Hunt's past on their trail. Joined by new allies and armed with the means to shut the Entity down for good, Hunt is in a race against time to prevent the world as we know it from changing forever.","genre_ids":[28,53,12],"media_type":"movie","popularity":40.8365,"vote_count":2580,"poster_path":"/z53D72EAOxGRqdr7KXXWp9dJiDe.jpg","release_date":"2025-05-17","vote_average":7.19,"backdrop_path":"/538U9snNc2fpnOmYXAPUh3zn31H.jpg","original_title":"Mission: Impossible - The Final Reckoning","original_language":"en"},{"id":1233413,"adult":false,"title":"Sinners","video":false,"overview":"Trying to leave their troubled lives behind, twin brothers return to their hometown to start again, only to discover that an even greater evil is waiting to welcome them back.","genre_ids":[27,28,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":37.799,"vote_count":3775,"poster_path":"/qTvFWCGeGXgBRaINLY1zqgTPSpn.jpg","release_date":"2025-04-16","vote_average":7.489,"backdrop_path":"/nAxGnGHOsfzufThz20zgmRwKur3.jpg","original_title":"Sinners","original_language":"en