dvertises for her safe return and offers to pay Rs.1.25 Lakhs to the finder. Four days later, Kammo returns and she is not the same anymore, she is more humble, sober, and respectful. Fully appreciative of this, Girdharilal agrees to get her married to Sumankumar. Just before the marriage, a man named Sagar approaches them - and it is this visit that will change their lives forever.","genre_ids":[10749,18,35],"popularity":0.1643,"vote_count":3,"poster_path":"/qLZyQFJhlpVdlEYTk3RMiWDXFg9.jpg","release_date":"1956-07-06","vote_average":7.333,"backdrop_path":"/hPOJcsmI0uypibRsek7hz9AOv4O.jpg","original_title":"चोरी चोरी","original_language":"hi"},{"id":48388,"adult":false,"title":"Dil Apna Aur Preet Parai","video":false,"overview":"A rich girl marries a doctor. Differences crop up between the two and starts to snowball wherein she returns to her father's house. Months later she returns only to find he is in love with a nurse.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"popularity":0.2172,"vote_count":2,"poster_path":"/9BOvIWE8KWdBSK4gUamXkwij9QP.jpg","release_date":"1960-01-01","vote_average":4.5,"backdrop_path":"/3agQXqAKp5PxR0BygbN2pHmr91L.jpg","original_title":"Dil Apna Aur Preet Parai","original_language":"hi"},{"id":48390,"adult":false,"title":"Gangaa Jamunaa Saraswathi","video":false,"overview":"Gangaa Jamunaa and Saraswathi the most pious rivers, create a unique holy merger, popularly known as \"Sangam\". Likewise the characters of our story Gangaa Jamunaa and Saraswathi desire to meet and merge in love of each other. Gangaa Jamunaa begin to love each other and pledge to become one, Saraswati silently loves Gangaa, and dedicates her life to him. However there are many, who would like to separate the happy lovers. There is Hansraj, who does it, and with the result Jamuna separates from Gangaa. Jamuna reaches Shanker's home, Shanker who already loved her becomes extremely happy finding Jamuna in his home. In the meantime Saraswati was about to come closer to Ganga. When Hansraj, who had earlier swindled the property of Ganga's father by illegal means wanted to get rid of the rightful owner Ganga, he got Ganga shot. Ganga was badly wounded and there was no hope of his survival.","genre_ids":[28,18,10749],"popularity":0.3814,"vote_count":6,"poster_path":"/cMOCDG5imInIKlx4tbFrH8JeL9w.jpg","release_date":"1988-12-23","vote_average":5,"backdrop_path":"/jrB6PdLBcf0N4nlMDuQIIUb4Gg9.jpg","original_title":"गंगा जमुना सरस्वती","original_language":"hi"},{"id":1109086,"adult":false,"title":"War 2","video":false,"overview":"Years ago Agent Kabir went rogue, became India’s greatest villain ever.  As he descends further into the deepest shadows... India sends its deadliest, most lethal agent after him, Agent Vikram  A Special Units Officer who is more than Kabir’s equal and a relentless Terminator driven by his own demons, determined to put a bullet into Kabir’s skull.","genre_ids":[28,12,53],"popularity":5.3267,"vote_count":56,"poster_path":"/fxxVbjhIOl8ZPS69dH8xeeuxvmh.jpg","release_date":"2025-08-13","vote_average":5.875,"backdrop_path":"/pKIRUTnwY3YYU9urSdsuobdcliP.jpg","original_title":"वॉर 2","original_language":"hi"},{"id":900838,"adult":false,"title":"The Bengal Files","video":false,"overview":"A criminal investigator uncovers a web of corruption during a missing person investigation, while a figure connected to the case reflects on the communal violence which broke out ahead of India's partition.","genre_ids":[18,36,53],"popularity":0.986,"vote_count":6,"poster_path":"/3gbZh1S735CLz7NwFRb7bycUWkP.jpg","release_date":"2025-09-05","vote_average":4.333,"backdrop_path":"/ncvfuh7OZG46Ohiw73RQfKVNecO.jpg","original_title":"The Bengal Files","original_language":"hi"},{"id":48569,"adult":false,"title":"Humko Deewana Kar Gaye","video":false,"overview":"Aditya, an engineer, travels to Canada for training. There he meets Jia, a beautiful woman from an influential family. Fate keeps pushing the pair together, and even though both are already betrothed to others